{"id":217,"date":"2017-02-12T08:58:10","date_gmt":"2017-02-12T08:58:10","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/?p=217"},"modified":"2017-03-09T16:25:00","modified_gmt":"2017-03-09T16:25:00","slug":"currencies","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/currencies\/","title":{"rendered":"Currencies"},"content":{"rendered":"<h4>Create new currency<\/h4>\n<p>To add new currency go to <strong>Setup\u00a0-&gt; Finance\u00a0-&gt; Currencies<\/strong> and click <strong>New Currency.<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Currency Code &#8211; Add currency code, make sure you add the valid currency\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/List_of_circulating_currencies\">ISO code<\/a>. The ISO Code will be used when sending the currency code to online payment gateways.<\/li>\n<li>Currency Symbol &#8211; Add currency symbol<\/li>\n<li>Click\u00a0Save<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>If this is your base currency<strong> you will need to mark it as base<\/strong> by clicking on the <strong>Star<\/strong>\u00a0icon.<\/p>\n<div><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/currencies-768x214.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"214\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/currencies-768x214.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/currencies-768x214-300x84.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/currencies-768x214-60x17.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/currencies-768x214-150x42.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><\/div>\n<p><strong>Perfex CRM by default record all transactions (invoices,estimates,expenses,proposals) in the base currency.<\/strong><\/p>\n<div class=\"st-alert st-alert-warning \">Changing the base\/customer currency after you record transactions is not possible.<\/div>\n<h4><b>Record transactions other then base currency<\/b><\/h4>\n<p>There is only 1 exception where changing the currency is possible when creating new proposal and the proposal is related to lead.<\/p>\n<div class=\"st-alert st-alert-info \">If you need to record the transaction in different currency you need to set <strong>customer currency.<\/strong><\/div>\n<p>Navigate to Customers-&gt; Click on the customer and set currency in the customer profile.<\/p>\n<p>Note that <strong>if the\u00a0customer have already recorded transactions you wont be able to change the currency.<\/strong> You need to delete all previous transactions to change the currency, once the transaction is recorded ability to change the customer currency will be disabled.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-348\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/customer-currency-1024x657.png\" alt=\"Customer Currency\" width=\"980\" height=\"629\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/customer-currency-1024x657.png 1024w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/customer-currency-300x193.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/customer-currency-768x493.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/customer-currency-60x39.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/customer-currency-150x96.png 150w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/customer-currency.png 1042w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 980px) 100vw, 980px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Try creating new eq. invoice and select the customer the currency will be auto changed\u00a0based on the currency you set for this customer.<\/p>\n<p>For all future\u00a0transactions for this customer the customer currency will be auto selected.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Create new currency To add new currency go to Setup\u00a0-&gt; Finance\u00